</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"17\" data-roll-max=\"20\">17-20</td><td class=\"col-10\">Trap or other trick designed to kill or capture creatures that enter the dungeon</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>General Dungeon Chambers</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"true\">[[/r d100]]</th><th class=\"col-10\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Purpose</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"1\" data-roll-max=\"1\">01</td><td class=\"col-10\">Antechamber</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"2\" data-roll-max=\"3\">02-03</td><td class=\"col-10\">Armory</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"4\" data-roll-max=\"4\">04</td><td class=\"col-10\">Audience chamber</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"5\" data-roll-max=\"5\">05</td><td class=\"col-10\">Aviary</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"6\" data-roll-max=\"7\">06-07</td><td class=\"col-10\">Banquet room</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"8\" data-roll-max=\"10\">08-10</td><td class=\"col-10\">Barracks</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"11\" data-roll-max=\"11\">11</td><td class=\"col-10\">Bath or latrine</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"12\" data-roll-max=\"12\">12</td><td class=\"col-10\">Bedroom</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"13\" data-roll-max=\"13\">13</td><td class=\"col-10\">Bestiary</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"14\" data-roll-max=\"16\">14-16</td><td class=\"col-10\">Cell</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"17\" data-roll-max=\"17\">17</td><td class=\"col-10\">Chantry</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"18\" data-roll-max=\"18\">18</td><td class=\"col-10\">Chapel</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 t